The Vice President of the United States, Joe Biden, spoke with Bahraini Crown Prince Salman bin Hamad al-Khalifa to express support for his efforts to initiate a National Dialogue on political reform. They acknowledged the importance of reaching out to the opposition and maintaining law and order for a productive dialogue to take place. The Vice President encouraged further outreach and meaningful reform that addresses the aspirations of all Bahrainis. Both agreed that a political solution is necessary for long-term stability in Bahrain.